Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - Implementation across all process variants where it occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait - Implementation per case, aggregated by country
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait - Implementation when followed by Completed + Resolved
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Time from Accepted + In Progress to Accepted + Wait - Implementation in variants containing both activities
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Elapsed time between Queued + Awaiting Assignment and Accepted + Wait - Implementation in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait - Implementation compared to the duration of Accepted + Wait - User in shared variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - User occurs

Name: Time of Accepted + Wait - Implementation when directly preceded by Accepted + In Progress
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Cycle Time of Accepted + Wait - Implementation in cases that also include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Total time for Accepted + Wait - Implementation in variants that end with Completed + Closed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Closed occurs

Name: Minimum time it takes Accepted + Wait - Implementation after the execution of Queued + Awaiting Assignment
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Average time until Accepted + Wait - Implementation is performed from case start in relevant variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Time from Accepted + Wait - Implementation to Completed + Resolved in high-frequency variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Elapsed time between Accepted + Wait - Implementation and Completed + In Call when both appear in a case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - Implementation in cases where Completed + In Call appears earlier in the trace
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs
